<BaseLayout title="Refunds — oriz" description="14-day no-questions refund policy for paid Oriz tiers." canonical="https://oriz.in/refunds/" sidebar={false}>
  <header class="spine page-head">
    <p class="eyebrow"><a href="/">oriz</a> / refunds</p>
    <h1>Refunds</h1>
    <p class="lede">14-day, no-questions refunds on every paid tier.</p>
  </header>
  <section class="spine prose">
    <p>Every Oriz tool is free to use. Paid tiers (Pro $5/mo, Max $15/mo) unlock higher quotas. If a paid tier doesn't fit, email <a href="mailto:hello@oriz.in">hello@oriz.in</a> within 14 days — we refund in full.</p>
    <p>Refunds are processed on the original payment rail (Razorpay for India, Lemon Squeezy for international). Typical landing time 3–7 business days.</p>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
